<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Helvetica;"><font color="#002cfd"><font size="5"><b><u>Bessacarr E410 - 2
berth Motorhome on Fiat Ducato 2.2 TDI.&nbsp;</u></b></font><font size="4"><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Helvetica;"><font color="#002cfd" size="4">2 travelling seats with
diagonal seat belts. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Helvetica;"><font color="#002cfd" size="4">Mid-lounge seats can be
converted into one double bed or used as 2 singles.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Helvetica;"><font color="#002cfd" size="4">Gas oven, grill and hob
with one electric ring.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Helvetica;"><font color="#002cfd" size="4">Built in microwave,<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Helvetica;"><font color="#002cfd" size="4">3 way function fridge.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Helvetica;"><font color="#002cfd" size="4">Bathroom including
shower and toilet.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Helvetica;"><font color="#002cfd" size="4">Gas and Electric
heating and hot water.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Helvetica;"><font color="#002cfd" size="4">Comes equipped with TV,
hook up and other extras.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Helvetica;"><font color="#002cfd" size="4">Built in front screens
on all cab windows&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Helvetica;"><font color="#002cfd" size="4">Electric step.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>

